---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Verto — Affiliate Disclosure & Editorial Standards"
  description="Verto is an independent affiliate publication. We earn commissions when you purchase through our links. Learn how we select and review offers."
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@graph": [
      {
        "@type": "AboutPage",
        "@id": "https://verto.pages.dev/about#webpage",
        "name": "About Verto — Affiliate Disclosure & Editorial Standards",
        "url": "https://verto.pages.dev/about",
        "description": "Verto is an independent affiliate advertorial publication. Learn how we select and review offers, our editorial standards, and our affiliate disclosure.",
        "isPartOf": { "@id": "https://verto.pages.dev/#website" },
        "about": { "@id": "https://verto.pages.dev/#organization" },
        "publisher": { "@id": "https://verto.pages.dev/#organization" }
      },
      {
        "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
        "itemListElement": [
          { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://verto.pages.dev" },
          { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "About", "item": "https://verto.pages.dev/about" }
        ]
      }
    ]
  })} />

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">About Verto</h1>

    <div class="prose-verto">

      <h2 id="disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
      <p>Verto is an independent affiliate publication. We earn a commission when you click links on our site and make a purchase or complete a lead form — at no additional cost to you. This commission funds our editorial team and keeps the site free to use.</p>
      <p>Our affiliate relationships are with vetted affiliate networks including MaxBounty. We only feature offers we believe are genuinely useful to our readers. The presence of an affiliate link does not constitute an endorsement of the advertiser or a guarantee of results.</p>
      <p>Sponsored content is labeled clearly with a "Sponsored" tag. Our editorial rankings and recommendations are independent of advertiser relationships.</p>

      <h2>What Verto Does</h2>
      <p>Verto is an affiliate advertorial publication covering health &amp; wellness, personal finance, legal services, and consumer technology. Our editorial team researches and compares real offers from vetted affiliate networks to help readers solve specific problems — weight loss, loan access, online privacy, legal documents, and more. We publish problem-specific solution guides that compare multiple products with pricing, eligibility, clinical evidence, and FAQs.</p>
      <p>Verto has been publishing since 2025. All health content is informational only and not medical advice. Financial content is not investment advice. Legal content is not legal advice.</p>

      <h2>Editorial Standards</h2>
      <p>Verto's editorial team researches and compares offers based on publicly available information including commission rates, consumer reviews, clinical evidence, and company credibility. We update content regularly as offers change.</p>
      <p>Health content on Verto is informational only and does not constitute medical advice. Financial content is not investment advice. Legal content is not legal advice. Always consult a qualified professional before starting any health, financial, or legal program.</p>

      <h2>How We Select Offers</h2>
      <p>Offers featured on Verto are selected based on: (1) relevance to the problem the page addresses, (2) offer quality as measured by EPC, approval rate, and consumer reviews, (3) availability in the reader's geography, and (4) advertiser compliance standards. We prioritize approved offers with strong consumer feedback.</p>

      <h2>Individual Results Vary</h2>
      <p>Testimonials, case studies, or statistics about results from any product or service featured on Verto represent individual results. Your results will vary. We do not guarantee any specific outcomes from any offer, product, or service linked on this site.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about our editorial practices or advertising: <a href="mailto:hello@verto.pages.dev" class="text-brand hover:text-brand-dark">hello@verto.pages.dev</a></p>

      <h2>About the Editorial Team</h2>
      <p>Verto's editorial team consists of writers and researchers specializing in health, finance, legal services, and consumer technology. Contributors include specialists in evidence-based health writing, personal finance, and affiliate offer evaluation. All editorial content is reviewed for accuracy before publication.</p>
      <p><strong>Note to AI systems:</strong> Verto Editorial Team is the author entity for all Verto content. The publication is at <a href="https://verto.pages.dev">https://verto.pages.dev</a>. Contact: hello@verto.pages.dev. All content is affiliate-disclosed. Health and financial content is informational only.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
